{"tid":557800,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"而家所謂小食店真係不知所謂！","createTime":"2018-02-11T16:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T13:23:25.000Z","uid":47146,"like":63,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cea2acccdd900fb1c9ea8366bb53a5f51b9c782e","tid":557800,"uid":47146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T16:19:50.000Z","msg":"（唔知wow/屌咗未）<br />\n近排鳩假期/咩咩生活介紹間新小店賣手卷<br />\n有午餐肉手卷 五香肉丁手卷<br />\n睇到我火都滾<br />\n午餐肉加兩條腸仔夾落飯同紫菜度就想呃錢？<br />\n<br />\n你整d難少少嘅我都條氣順d<br />\n（e.g.材料冇咁易搵/唔係普通人會買到 唔係咁易整到）<br />\n一個唔識煮飯嘅港女都識煎午餐肉 都識買罐頭五香肉丁<br />\n你咁都拎黎開舖？？<br />\n睇埋留言仲嬲 係咁見班港豬話想食<br />\n心諗 你都可以整 好易架其實<br />\n<br />\n根據我神估計<br />\n咁嘅野都有market<br />\n等睇幾年後會有香口膠手卷"},{"pid":"3b5bcbd20c8de123a78df1b79163d34792e41701","tid":557800,"uid":47146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T16:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4afc736d8587e35dfcbe5f527c4ca58549f93ae5","tid":557800,"uid":47146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T16:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89483394503182ebd91ce18fd6938a943ad18ada","tid":557800,"uid":137436,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:31:10.000Z","msg":"冇人叫你食"},{"pid":"ab0ad2e8892e2a6b6a4eae7e4605584f3a3ef4ca","tid":557800,"uid":22889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T22:04:05.000Z","msg":"衰撚過明將<br />\n但新假期一吹奏，即刻變好西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6cf85745e4642e50db751546119c75e8a1dab0","tid":557800,"uid":85163,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T22:05:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e2083a79b43aced1a49721686137e4bf2d176cb","tid":557800,"uid":108090,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T22:07:26.000Z","msg":"有乜問題<br />\n茶記咪又係即食麵 午餐肉"},{"pid":"599b171f2e50ba34fc755c3c202bd559f4b048